   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["# Driver Not Starting Troubleshooting", "**Symptoms:** Connection refused, driver pod crashloop"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": ["import kubernetes", "k8s = kubernetes.config.load_kube_config()", "v1 = kubernetes.client.CoreV1Api(api_client=k8s)"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## Диагностика driver host", "Проверить FQDN сервиса"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": ["NAMESPACE = \"spark\"", "service = v1.read_namespaced_service(NAMESPACE, \"spark-41-connect\")", "print(f\"Service FQDN: {service.spec.cluster_ip}.{NAMESPACE}.svc.cluster.local\")"]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": ["## Решение", "```bash", "# Для K8s backend", "helm upgrade spark-connect charts/spark-4.1 -n spark \\  --set connect.driver.host=\"\" \\  --reuse-values", "", "# Для Standalone backend", "helm upgrade spark-connect charts/spark-4.1 -n spark \\  --set connect.driver.host=spark-41-connect.spark.svc.cluster.local \\  --reuse-values", "```", "", "**Рекомендации:**", "- K8s backend: driver.host пустой", "- Standalone: FQDN сервиса Connect"]
  },
 ],
